            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美國財長貝森特稱讚赤字佔GDP比率下降 預計退稅潮將至\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"671\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bxY8IPfbx7nYm8IpJdnXRw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY3MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/1d8aa850-a56d-11f0-9dff-05ed2f182eee\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美國財長貝森特稱讚赤字佔GDP比率下降 預計退稅潮將至</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
